==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Traumatism
<hw>Trau"ma*tism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A wound or injury directly produced by causes external to the body;
also, violence producing a wound or injury; <as>as, rupture of the
stomach caused by <ex>traumatism</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traunce</ent>⟦br⟧
